text: This movie has "guilty pleasure" vibe for me. ¬†AND THAT IS NOT A BAD THING. ¬†Remember that a good movie and an entertaining movie are not always the same thing. A movie doesn't always have to be a 5 star experience. ¬†Sometimes, you just want a Big Mac, and not a 5 star fancy dinner. ¬†I do enjoy movies that I can shut off my brain, suspend my disbelief, and just have fun. ¬†Van Helsing, I Frankenstein, the Resident Evil series, Street Fighter (Van Dame), the Blade trilogy, and League of Extraordinary Gentlemen are all bad movies....but entertaining and fun.  This movie looks pretty badass and entertaining. ¬†It also looks cheesy and hokey. ¬†Above all else...it looks like it will be fun! ¬†Vin Diesel is in a select group of actors who have an immunity to bad dialogue. ¬†Actors who can say the corniest, cheesiest, and awful dialogue...and sill make it look and sound cool. ¬†Arnold Schwarzenegger, and Keanue Reeves are also in that club. ¬†So Vin Diesel is in an elite class in my opinion. ¬†This one I am excited for!
